---
title: Middle Eastern Mango Chicken & Garlic Rice with Tomato Salsa & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Enjoy the mild, aromatic flavours inspired by Ethiopia in a meal that everyone will love! Tender chicken gets a light
Berbere spice coating, which goes perfectly with garlic rice. Then, finish it off with a creamy herb yoghurt to cover all
your bases.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
